<h3>Factions</h3>

<h4>Japan</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Faction locations can be razed</li>
    <li>Discarded instead of becoming foundation</li>
    <li>Any time during turn: deploy any number of workers as samurai to faction locations</li>
    <li>Max 1 samurai per location</li>
    <li>A samurai increases required raze tokens by 1</li>
    <li>Samurai are not discarded during cleanup</li>
</ul>

<h4>Atlanteans</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Tech tokens
        <ul>
            <li>Basic: repeat production, double the feature's effect, or allow additional action</li>
            <li>Advanced scoring: +1vp each time this location produces/triggers/activates</li>
            <li>Advanced defense: acts same as regular defense token, location cannot have both</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Production phase: receive N defense tokens</li>
    <li>May place any number of tech tokens during turn, before or after action</li>
    <li>Common locations: max 1 tech token per type (max 3 total)</li>
    <li>Cannot move tech tokens once placed</li>
    <li>Do not discard tech tokens during cleanup</li>
    <li>After razing,
        <ul>
            <li><i>Basic</i> tech tokens return to player</li>
            <li><i>Advanced</i> tech tokens return to supply</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Non-Atlanteans can only use tech tokens as activation costs</li>
</ul>

<h4>Aztecs</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Max 1 blessing per color, for each player</li>
    <li>Tricolor token
        <ul>
            <li>May count as 1 of brown/gray/red for each action</li>
            <li>Color can change for each action</li>
            <li>Does not count toward color limit</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Pray X
        <ul>
            <li>Draw X common cards</li>
            <li>"Announce": pick color <i>before</i> cards are revealed</li>
            <li>"Choose": pick color <i>after</i> cards are revealed</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Using blessings during pray (blessing is not consumed)
        <ul>
            <li>Guarantee: skip the pray action, count matching blessing colors instead</li>
            <li>Augment: blessings that match the pray action count as 1 extra of that color
                <br />
                Example:
                <br />
                <span style="margin-left: 20px;">card: Pray 5, gain for black/pink/golden</span>
                <br />
                <span style="margin-left: 20px;">Draw: pink, pink, blue, golden, gray (no black)</span>
                <br />
                <span style="margin-left: 20px;">Result: +1 for a pink blessing, +1 for a golden blessing, +1 for a <u>black</u> blessing</span>
                <br />
                Note: no blessings would trigger if 0 cards matched
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>

<h4>Amazons</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Foundation from production/deal: add a common card as a foundation, do not take wood</li>
    <li>Amazons shuffle faction cards back into the deck when used for a build cost</li>
    <li>Conquered enemy locations that are used to pay a cost go back to that enemy's faction deck</li>
</ul>
